                  "content": "All donations made through this website are voluntary and non-refundable. Donation processing is handled securely by Stripe. We do not store your payment information. Funds are allocated as described on the website: 40% to cancer research, 30% to patient support, 20% to prevention programs, and 10% to trail operations.",
